@startuml DeleteCourses
|Admin|
start
:1. Open course list;
:2. Select course to delete;
:3. Confirm deletion;
|CourseDashboard|
:4. Send delete request;
|CourseController|
:5. Verify course exists;
:6. Delete course from backend;
|Database|
:7. Remove course record;
|CourseController|
:8. Return success;
|CourseDashboard|
:9. Display confirmation;
:10. Refresh course list;
stop
@enduml
